reviewText: While the tape itself seems fine, the cover was not only in bad shape but was not the cover advertised.
Bought this for a friend because he needed the inappropriate case nostalgia. He gave it 5 stars.
The vhs was in good condition but the case was in bad shape

Since I went to some Goodwill store, I looked on the VHS cover case and there is tower that looks like a you-know-what. Whoever draw this tower that looks like a private part, someone would get fired for drawing a tower so bad.
